│ their uses. A conservative fix is to bail out from vectorizing insert sequences if collected build instructions/operands are from different basic blocks than the seed insert. I will    │
│ inject a dominance check into vectorizeInsertValueInst and vectorizeInsertElementInst to require all parts be in the same block as the seed, preventing invalid dominance. Then submit   │
│ the patch.                                                                                                                                                                               │
